description: Therapy Coffee & Tea is a full service mobile espresso bar/cafe. Bringing the very best coffee and teas from Austin and across the nation to you. Give us a call, and let Therapy Coffee & Tea make your next event a moment worth remembering.  Don't have space for a truck but still want delicious fresh coffee on site? No worries. We've got you covered. Our pop up cafe fits just about anywhere! We can set up on the 20th floor office suite you work in, that awesome backyard you worked so hard on, or even in a stunning ballroom. You name it. We can  make amazing coffee and tea almost anywhere!
name: Therapy Coffee & Tea
